name: “Aether”
description: Get this “Aether” NFT when you collect all the other elements before this one  Aristotle also suggested that there was another element, aether, because it seemed strange that the stars would be made out of earthly elements. He would be surprised to learn that they are in fact made up of many elements found on earth, and are so hot they could be said to be on fire all the time! I made one track that picks up where the last nft’s music leaves off
